data.description: Nestled in the heart of the peaceful Virginia Beach community, this charming 4-bedroom, 1-bathroom ranch-style home offers a perfect blend of modern comfort and classic elegance. With a recently updated kitchen and bathroom, this property is a true gem. The updated kitchen boasts sleek countertops, and ample cabinet space, making it the perfect kitchen. The bathroom has also been tastefully upgraded with modern fixtures and finishes. One of the standout features of this home is its spacious front and backyard. The generous front yard offers curb appeal and a tranquil space for outdoor relaxation. The expansive backyard is perfect for hosting gatherings, gardening, or simply enjoying the sunshine in privacy. Situated on a quiet street, this residence provides a serene environment. It's an ideal location for those seeking peace and tranquility while still being close to all the amenities that Virginia Beach has to offer.
